            <ul class="bullet-list">
            	<li><strong>Nursing Sleep Bra:</strong> As you adjust to your post-pregnancy body, a nursing sleep bra will be the most comfortable right after you give birth. These bras offer full coverage, light support and a pull-down nursing design for quick, easy night and early morning feedings.</li>
				<li><strong>Clip-Down Nursing Bra:</strong> Once you have become more acclimated with your nursing routine, clip-down nursing bras will make feeding times a breeze. They are available in seamless and underwire designs, depending on your comfort level and bra size.</li>
				<li><strong>Shaping Briefs:</strong> It may take a little time for your belly to go down, so the best <a href="{{ENV_HOSTNAME}}/shop/womens-clothing/panties/Brand/Motherhood%20Maternity?id=55805">post pregnancy underwear</a> to wear after you recuperate from giving birth will be shaping briefs. They will smooth out your tummy, offer great support and help you get back into your pre-pregnancy clothes.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

